{
  "stem": "868.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This went on for quite a while until the archbishop told Don Giovanni that things are getting much too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Don Casini was still held prisoner by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If they catch him, Don Giovanni, it would compromise the entire Catholic institutions in France.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he ordered him to leave town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, Don Giovanni was considering leaving town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he couldn't, or didn't want to, abandon his women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He decided to transfer them all with him to his city of birth, Treviso, in the north.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But he couldn't very well take all 12 at the same time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You must remember that at that time Italy was in the middle of a serious war, meaning daily bombardments on train tracks, train stations, cities, towns, and roads, plus, fascist brigades all over.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So the idea was to attract as little attention as possible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he decided to take them two or three at a-- at a time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he made four trips from Florence to Treviso, back to Florence, back to Treviso, each time taking two or three.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's an amusing incident connected with this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he was under surveillance, at one time he decided to go in civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These priests were dressed, not like you see them here, in long one piece black cassocks, with 33 buttons all the way down-- 33 being the age of Christ at which he died-- very severe attire, with a flat black hat, large rim.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So since he was under a surveillance, he decided to go in civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On that trip, he took with him a lady that was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her husband had been caught with us and departed with my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she had a small child, Harry [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was her name at the time, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
